## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| `Lemonade Server not available` | Run `lemonade-server serve` — `localhost:13305` is auto-discovered |
| `lemonade-server pull` fails | Check disk space; retry; verify network access |
| Schema not found | Check `$UFORGE_SCHEMA_DIR`, verify `.json` files exist |
| Dimension mismatch | Ensure embedding model matches vector column dimensions (768 vs 4096) |
| Whisper not loaded in RAM | First transcription call triggers load; subsequent calls are fast. `GET /api/v1/health` shows loaded models |
| Transcription error: "Could not open audio data" | Audio bytes empty or not a valid WAV/MP3/OGG |
